火再也控制不住，果兩個釘，亦由軟既棉&shy;花糖變為硬既橡皮糖啦！</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b821eb418c5f07764b8054208a869d2daf6c4ca1","tid":126161,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"幫唔幫裝icq"},{"pid":"7a4d319005b8113e6967c7c9c57d77b183c20f8b","tid":126161,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"參考：<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%81%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%99%BANet%E7%9A%84&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69f1035e\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個計劃只係一年限定，只且仲係2008年金融海嘯後，港府提出嘅短期就業措拖之一。"},{"pid":"3c9b403b3e8f72330f9ec225e6aa31d58da1241c","tid":126161,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>參考：<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%81%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%99%BANet%E7%9A%84&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69f1035e\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個計劃只係一年限定，只且仲係2008年金融海嘯後，港府提出嘅短期就業措拖之一。</blockquote><br />\n好奇問 有冇人真係做過受助者"},{"pid":"004417f3d592e7bfd6153f0baf0c872fb9575823","tid":126161,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>參考：<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%81%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%99%BANet%E7%9A%84&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69f1035e\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個計劃只係一年限定，只且仲係2008年金融海嘯後，港府提出嘅短期就業措拖之一。</blockquote><br />\n好奇問 有冇人真係做過受助者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果時中七老母買左部電腦比我down pastpaper<br />\n成世人第一部 乜都唔識<br />\n跟住就叫左個上黎 叫佢教我連上網<br />\n<br />\n上到黎 女仔黎wor 應該大學生黎<br />\n跟住就入房整部機<br />\n首先就set返個netvigator config先<br />\n跟住佢見我down pp d野佢又識<br />\n就話第日我讀書有咩唔明都可以搵佢"},{"pid":"d23124452db21ee2ae438afb0364d9e30d00aab3","tid":126161,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫唔幫裝icq</blockquote><br />\n+200"},{"pid":"da12c195a3fe0da08eeea76248a202cf9b9ec145","tid":126161,"uid":72277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>參考：<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%81%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%99%BANet%E7%9A%84&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69f1035e\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個計劃只係一年限定，只且仲係2008年金融海嘯後，港府提出嘅短期就業措拖之一。</blockquote><br />\n好奇問 有冇人真係做過受助者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果時中七老母買左部電腦比我down pastpaper<br />\n成世人第一部 乜都唔識<br />\n跟住就叫左個上黎 叫佢教我連上網<br />\n<br />\n上到黎 女仔黎wor 應該大學生黎<br />\n跟住就入房整部機<br />\n首先就set返個netvigator config先<br />\n跟住佢見我down pp d野佢又識<br />\n就話第日我讀書有咩唔明都可以搵佢</blockquote><br />\n我等緊下文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cadaf20ba3379ca2859a608f14b316436f4cc9","tid":126161,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>參考：<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E5%81%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%99%BANet%E7%9A%84&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=69f1035e\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/做個智Net的</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個計劃只係一年限定，只且仲係2008年金融海嘯後，港府提出嘅短期就業措拖之一。</blockquote><br />\n好奇問 有冇人真係做過受助者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果時中七老母買左部電腦比我down pastpaper<br />\n成世人第一部 乜都唔識<br />\n跟住就叫左個上黎 叫佢教我連上網<br />\n